1
00:00:09,343 --> 00:00:14,164
Akhirnya, aku pilih sakiti orang yang paling aku sayang.

2
00:00:14,502 --> 00:00:16,834
Semata-mata nak lindungi seorang lagi yang aku sayang.

3
00:00:17,084 --> 00:00:19,774
Jadi, apa benda pertama kau bagi P'Fah dulu?

4
00:00:20,125 --> 00:00:21,528
- Apa benda sial tu?
- Sandwic dan susu coklat.

5
00:00:22,143 --> 00:00:25,263
Kau betul-betul rasa ini idea yang bagus?

6
00:00:25,802 --> 00:00:29,201
Mestilah. Dah sampai sini, tak boleh undur sekarang.

7
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:31,120
Apa, kau ingat aku ni rider penghantar ke?

8
00:00:32,302 --> 00:00:36,752
Taklah teruk sangat.
Kalau setakat ni saja, biarlah.

9
00:00:41,297 --> 00:00:42,805
Tolong bagi ini pada pemilik surat tu.

10
00:00:43,611 --> 00:00:44,810
Baik.

11
00:00:52,277 --> 00:00:54,016
Jadi... kau suka dia, ya?

12
00:00:54,885 --> 00:00:56,429
Belum sampai tahap suka lagi.

13
00:00:56,791 --> 00:00:58,139
Aku cuma nak kenal dia dengan lebih dekat.

14
00:01:01,263 --> 00:01:02,749
Kau tahu siapa dia?

15
00:01:03,048 --> 00:01:04,019
Tak.

16
00:01:04,179 --> 00:01:06,520
Kau tak nak tahu?

17
00:01:07,321 --> 00:01:11,346
Tengok dia suruh orang lain sampaikan,
jelas dia tak nak aku tahu.

18
00:01:11,626 --> 00:01:14,343
Kalau dia tak nak aku tahu, aku pun takkan tahu.

19
00:01:14,943 --> 00:01:16,202
Tapi aku memang nak tahu.

20
00:01:17,546 --> 00:01:20,388
Fah, aku nak tanya kau.

21
00:01:21,139 --> 00:01:23,570
Biasanya ramai orang bagi kau barang.

22
00:01:24,629 --> 00:01:26,717
Jadi kenapa yang ni lain macam, ha?

23
00:01:29,379 --> 00:01:30,520
Aku tak tahu macam mana nak jelaskan.

24
00:01:32,774 --> 00:01:36,069
Bila baca mesej tu, aku rasa tenang.

25
00:01:36,755 --> 00:01:39,355
Mesej dia ringkas, biasa saja.

26
00:01:40,518 --> 00:01:43,792
Dia tak pernah minta apa-apa atau harap balasan.

27
00:01:45,031 --> 00:01:47,117
Dia cuma harap aku okey dan sihat.

28
00:01:47,548 --> 00:01:48,991
Itu saja.

29
00:02:02,404 --> 00:02:06,755
Rasa macam aku boleh melayang saja.

30
00:02:07,152 --> 00:02:08,480
Aku faham.

31
00:02:09,955 --> 00:02:12,112
Kau rasa P'Fah tahu itu kau?

32
00:02:13,151 --> 00:02:14,508
Yang dia suka kau?

33
00:02:16,065 --> 00:02:17,374
Atau dia suka orang dalam surat tu?

34
00:02:24,511 --> 00:02:26,512
Kalau dia rasa senang dengan orang dalam surat tu,

35
00:02:26,656 --> 00:02:27,980
itu bukan benda buruk pun, kan?

36
00:02:28,854 --> 00:02:30,488
Sebab Typhoon yang sebenar—

37
00:02:30,871 --> 00:02:32,905
nak bercakap dengan P'Fah pun tak berani.

38
00:02:33,472 --> 00:02:35,078
Tapi orang dalam surat tu boleh buat.

39
00:02:36,598 --> 00:02:37,582
- Phoon.
- Hmm?

40
00:02:38,454 --> 00:02:39,616
Boleh aku tanya kau sesuatu?

41
00:02:40,531 --> 00:02:41,687
Sekadar andaian.

42
00:02:42,023 --> 00:02:42,893
Kalau hari ini—

43
00:02:43,185 --> 00:02:44,518
ayah kau tak terlibat langsung,

44
00:02:45,807 --> 00:02:47,597
kau masih akan cuba rapat dengan P'Fah?

45
00:02:51,130 --> 00:02:52,674
Aku rasa aku akan—

46
00:02:53,183 --> 00:02:54,961
jaga P'Fah dengan lebih baik.

47
00:02:55,626 --> 00:03:01,287
Bukan setakat tulis surat, bukan setakat beli barang dan suruh dia jaga diri.

48
00:03:02,554 --> 00:03:03,976
Bagus, maew.

49
00:03:05,751 --> 00:03:09,517
Tapi jujur, aku rasa P'Fah tetap akan suka kau.

50
00:03:09,949 --> 00:03:12,198
Walaupun dia tahu kau yang tulis surat-surat tu.

51
00:03:12,616 --> 00:03:17,543
Sebab P'Fah mungkin suka kau yang penyayang
dan dia tahu kau betul-betul sayang dia.

52
00:03:24,321 --> 00:03:27,648
Hoi, berhenti. Phoon dah nak meletup.

53
00:03:28,195 --> 00:03:29,151
Kau betul-betul maksudkan tu?

54
00:03:30,155 --> 00:03:31,288
Nampak? Bukti.

55
00:03:33,909 --> 00:03:36,942
Mungkin dia cuma belikan untuk semua orang.

56
00:03:37,091 --> 00:03:41,848
Alah, mana mungkin P'Fah belikan untuk semua?
Ramai sangat orang bagi dia barang.

57
00:03:42,171 --> 00:03:44,580
Mesti orang yang istimewa.

58
00:03:46,019 --> 00:03:48,173
Apa pun, P'Fah suka kau.

59
00:03:48,477 --> 00:03:49,798
Kau memihak aku ke?

60
00:03:50,481 --> 00:03:52,334
Ya, sikitlah.

61
00:03:52,617 --> 00:03:56,623
Kenapa tak? Aku kawan kau.
Memang aku kena sokong kau habis-habisan.

62
00:03:56,791 --> 00:04:00,357
North pun sokong kau macam tu—mana boleh aku kalah?

63
00:04:00,562 --> 00:04:04,082
Mungkin sekarang dia dah buat “sihir cinta” pada P'Fah untuk kau.

64
00:04:05,885 --> 00:04:11,084
Baguslah. Aku rasa suasana jadi lebih cerah entah kenapa.

65
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:13,373
Kau dah tak nampak macam kucing mengantuk dah.

66
00:05:54,651 --> 00:05:57,785
Nampak? Aku dah cakap rancangan ni jadi.
Korang je tak percaya aku.

67
00:05:57,979 --> 00:06:00,010
Hah? Rancangan kau?

68
00:06:00,217 --> 00:06:01,456
Itu rancangan Dao.

69
00:06:01,583 --> 00:06:02,838
- Betul?
- Ya.

70
00:06:02,974 --> 00:06:07,063
Tapi aku yang buat rancangan tu 80% berjaya.

71
00:06:07,493 --> 00:06:10,986
Dan kau tahu siapa yang cari “Cupid penghantar” tu?

72
00:06:11,297 --> 00:06:12,195
Aku.

73
00:06:13,715 --> 00:06:16,167
Aku ni hensem gila.

74
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:18,300
Dan berbakat juga.

75
00:06:19,069 --> 00:06:20,967
Dan aku tak boleh buat apa-apa pasal tu.

76
00:06:21,505 --> 00:06:23,345
Menyampah.

77
00:06:23,555 --> 00:06:25,496
Dah. Naik sini cepat—drama sangat.

78
00:06:25,862 --> 00:06:27,022
Orang ni.

79
00:06:28,152 --> 00:06:30,134
Tapi kau tahu apa masalah sekarang?

80
00:06:30,554 --> 00:06:34,662
Masalahnya Phoon tak percaya P'Fah betul-betul suka dia.

81
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:37,125
Apa kau merepek ni?

82
00:06:37,811 --> 00:06:41,325
Sekarang ni aku rasa P'Fah dah siap nak buat perarakan pertunangan.

83
00:06:41,417 --> 00:06:42,468
Wah.

84
00:06:43,191 --> 00:06:47,198
Tapi aku dah cukup “spoiler”—kau yang raja spoiler sebenar.

85
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:49,431
Apa kau cakap ni?

86
00:06:49,650 --> 00:06:53,020
P'Fah tahu kau yang tulis surat tu?

87
00:06:58,343 --> 00:07:01,197
Tak, mestilah tak. Macam mana dia nak tahu?

88
00:07:02,328 --> 00:07:05,219
Tapi mana tahu—Phoon orang yang rapat dengan dia.

89
00:07:05,604 --> 00:07:08,554
P'Tonfah tahu kau suka dia?

90
00:07:11,971 --> 00:07:14,275
Aku rasa P'Fah tahu aku suka dia.

91
00:07:15,001 --> 00:07:16,133
Aku rasa—

92
00:07:16,568 --> 00:07:18,131
dia cuma anggap aku adik saja.

93
00:07:18,712 --> 00:07:19,527
Hoi.

94
00:07:20,288 --> 00:07:23,100
Kenapa kau anggap P'Fah cuma fikir kau sebagai adik?

95
00:07:23,903 --> 00:07:24,711
Ya.

96
00:07:25,441 --> 00:07:27,808
Mungkin sebab kami kenal sangat lama.

97
00:07:28,785 --> 00:07:33,205
Macam dia asyik cuba letak satu batas.

98
00:07:33,697 --> 00:07:35,731
Dan aku tak pernah langgar batas tu.

99
00:07:36,386 --> 00:07:39,591
Tunggu—kalau P'Fah tahu kau yang tulis surat tu...

100
00:07:39,902 --> 00:07:42,122
Tak ke dia akan letak batas tu lagi?

101
00:07:42,928 --> 00:07:47,306
Sebab tu aku tak nak dia tahu itu aku.

102
00:07:47,842 --> 00:07:50,410
Jadi kau langsung tak terfikir nak langgar batas tu?

103
00:07:51,348 --> 00:07:52,240
Ya.

104
00:07:57,194 --> 00:07:58,588
Aku...

105
00:07:59,490 --> 00:08:00,884
Aku takut kehilangan P'Fah.

106
00:08:01,562 --> 00:08:05,333
Kau takut hilang P'Fah, tapi kau tak takut dia jatuh hati pada orang lain?

107
00:08:08,823 --> 00:08:10,100
Mestilah aku takut.

108
00:08:10,334 --> 00:08:12,499
Fikir pasal tu pun dah buat aku sakit.

109
00:08:15,914 --> 00:08:16,949
Jadi kita nak buat apa?

110
00:08:17,395 --> 00:08:19,358
Aku rasa cuma ada satu cara.

111
00:08:20,850 --> 00:08:21,727
Ada?

112
00:08:22,001 --> 00:08:23,352
Iaitu—

113
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,684
- Pergi je!
- Hoi! Kau buat aku terkejut.

114
00:08:26,157 --> 00:08:27,900
Perjuangkan saja. Kau kena lawan.

115
00:08:28,044 --> 00:08:29,078
Lawan atau tak?

116
00:08:29,385 --> 00:08:30,274
Lawan.

117
00:08:30,629 --> 00:08:32,542
Hoi, lemah sangat. Lawan atau tak!!!

118
00:08:33,031 --> 00:08:34,488
Lawan!

119
00:08:34,825 --> 00:08:38,260
Aku akan buat P'Fah tahu betapa aku sayang dia.

120
00:08:38,885 --> 00:08:41,588
Ha, betul. Bagus. Lawan!!!

121
00:08:41,834 --> 00:08:43,128
Lawan!

122
00:08:43,188 --> 00:08:46,118
Yang ni bising, yang tu lembut sangat.

123
00:08:49,490 --> 00:08:51,620
- Kau ni selalu rosakkan mood.
- Tengok diri kau dulu.

124
00:08:57,011 --> 00:08:58,528
Apa kau buat, P'Hill?

125
00:08:58,734 --> 00:08:59,802
Nampak macam aku tak?

126
00:09:00,465 --> 00:09:03,048
Comel, tapi kau tak patut lukis kat sini.

127
00:09:03,482 --> 00:09:05,063
Supaya kau ingat aku masa kau belajar.

128
00:09:05,271 --> 00:09:07,678
Alah, walau aku tak belajar pun, aku tetap ingat kau.

129
00:09:08,484 --> 00:09:12,515
Wah, awalnya kau datang—aku ingat kau serius nak belajar.

130
00:09:13,202 --> 00:09:15,734
Rupanya kau datang nak lepak dengan—

131
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:18,140
- Apa?
- Diamlah.

132
00:09:19,825 --> 00:09:22,380
- Kawan aku cari aku. Aku pergi kelas dulu, P'.
- Mm.

133
00:09:22,488 --> 00:09:24,091
- Belajar rajin-rajin, okey?
- Ya.

134
00:09:25,103 --> 00:09:26,955
Pastikan kau makan juga, P'Hill.

135
00:09:27,921 --> 00:09:28,820
Aku pergi dulu.

136
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,952
- Mm, bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

137
00:09:51,005 --> 00:09:53,312
Kau datang awal ni—nak ambil sesuatu ke?

138
00:09:53,887 --> 00:09:54,714
Ya.

139
00:09:55,428 --> 00:09:56,588
Mesti penting sangat, ya?

140
00:09:59,891 --> 00:10:00,813
Ya.

141
00:10:01,322 --> 00:10:02,830
Memang penting sangat.

142
00:10:16,168 --> 00:10:18,816
"Penting sangat, ya?" "Ya, penting sangat."

143
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:21,032
Sampai macam tu, ya.

144
00:10:23,275 --> 00:10:25,884
Ship yang aku sokong sentiasa lancar, tak henti.

145
00:10:26,047 --> 00:10:27,825
Sekarang giliran kau.

146
00:10:29,934 --> 00:10:32,792
- Berhenti usik aku dah.
- Ooh, ada orang suka rupanya.

147
00:10:32,885 --> 00:10:35,394
Okey, okey.

148
00:10:35,419 --> 00:10:37,051
Kau selalu kasar bila kau malu.

149
00:10:38,838 --> 00:10:41,124
Sikit pun tak boleh usik.

150
00:10:41,385 --> 00:10:44,023
Kau gembira, ya. Kau malu, ya.

151
00:10:45,142 --> 00:10:47,303
Pelajar, sila duduk dengan betul.

152
00:11:06,048 --> 00:11:09,401
Selamat menjamu selera. Semoga hari anda baik.

153
00:11:32,976 --> 00:11:35,663
Wah, kau lalu je tanpa pandang aku pun.

154
00:11:36,682 --> 00:11:39,860
Ha, macam tu—banyakkan senyum.

155
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:20,296
Angkat sikit kepala tu. Nak aku cakap dengan tengkuk kau?

156
00:12:20,933 --> 00:12:22,454
North.

157
00:12:22,825 --> 00:12:23,921
Suara kau pecah.

158
00:12:24,672 --> 00:12:27,924
Wei, jantung aku nak tercabut ni.

159
00:12:28,942 --> 00:12:30,331
Bertenang, maew.

160
00:12:30,530 --> 00:12:32,226
Nak coklat? Mungkin membantu.

161
00:12:32,564 --> 00:12:34,202
Aku dah tak nak coklat.

162
00:12:34,317 --> 00:12:38,069
Oh? Dah tak nak coklat orang lain?

163
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:42,038
Sekarang cuma coklat P'Fah je?

164
00:12:42,068 --> 00:12:45,660
- Kau betul-betul tak nak berhenti usik aku, ya?
- Kelakar bila kau malu.

165
00:12:46,970 --> 00:12:51,597
Wei, ni macam mengurat dalam mesej ke? Atau—

166
00:12:51,997 --> 00:12:53,127
aku je yang perasan lebih?

167
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,210
Tengok mulut aku.

168
00:12:56,450 --> 00:12:58,303
P'Fah tengah mengurat kau.

169
00:12:58,548 --> 00:12:59,373
Faham?

170
00:13:00,318 --> 00:13:03,885
Mula-mula aku ingat kami cuma sahabat pena.

171
00:13:04,370 --> 00:13:08,420
Mana boleh setakat cakap je? Aku dah cakap—kena teruskan.

172
00:13:08,771 --> 00:13:10,548
Kau nak kekal dalam zon selamat macam ni?

173
00:13:10,850 --> 00:13:13,139
Kalau ya, kau akan terperangkap dalam zon tu selamanya.

174
00:13:13,940 --> 00:13:15,020
Aku tahu.

175
00:13:15,728 --> 00:13:16,724
Bagi aku masa sikit.

176
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:18,537
Alah, buat macam perlukan masa sangat.

177
00:13:18,782 --> 00:13:20,848
Kau kata kau nak mengurat P'Fah.

178
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:23,693
Tengok ni—sekarang P'Fah pula yang mengurat kau.

179
00:13:23,860 --> 00:13:25,586
Dan kau buat dia suka kau dulu macam ni—

180
00:13:26,586 --> 00:13:27,917
kau nak buat apa?

181
00:13:28,933 --> 00:13:30,328
Apa maksud kau, suka aku dulu?

182
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,380
Wah.

183
00:13:31,471 --> 00:13:34,530
Jadi kau nak biar “manis macam kau” terlepas?

184
00:13:34,677 --> 00:13:41,357
Cakap je—“Aku lebih manis dari coklat yang kau bagi.”

185
00:13:41,490 --> 00:13:43,792
Selitkan pujian sikit, mungkin.

186
00:13:43,922 --> 00:13:44,865
Kenapa tak cuba?

187
00:13:45,842 --> 00:13:49,389
Aku pun tak tahu hubungan kami nak ke mana.

188
00:13:49,968 --> 00:13:51,257
Dan pasal ayah aku juga.

189
00:13:53,010 --> 00:13:55,730
Apa pun jadi, aku tak boleh dedah aku penulis surat tu.

190
00:13:56,114 --> 00:13:57,096
Jadi kau—

191
00:13:57,417 --> 00:13:59,628
nak buat dia suka kau lepas tu hilang?

192
00:14:00,668 --> 00:14:01,834
Kejamnya.

193
00:14:02,254 --> 00:14:04,340
Aku tak pernah kata aku nak hilang.

194
00:14:04,518 --> 00:14:06,749
Kau dah pernah hilang dari P'Fah sekali dulu.

195
00:14:07,125 --> 00:14:08,749
Kau nak buat lagi kali ni?

196
00:14:09,075 --> 00:14:11,114
P'Fah akan terluka sangat.

197
00:14:11,613 --> 00:14:13,616
Aku tak nak ia berakhir macam dulu lagi.

198
00:14:14,485 --> 00:14:15,955
Aku tak nak tengok P'Fah terluka.

199
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:18,229
Selesaikan hal ayah kau dulu.

200
00:14:18,585 --> 00:14:22,242
Dia cuma takut kau beritahu orang kau anak orang lain, dia malu.

201
00:14:22,601 --> 00:14:24,402
Itu memang salah dia sendiri.

202
00:14:24,771 --> 00:14:26,589
Kenapa dia buat benda tu dari awal?

203
00:14:26,980 --> 00:14:28,540
Nak aku cakap dengan dia untuk kau?

204
00:14:29,198 --> 00:14:30,580
Lupakan dulu hal tu.

205
00:14:30,902 --> 00:14:36,454
Ya, jangan fikir sangat. Cuba ikut hati kau kadang-kadang. Hidup kau.

206
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:38,350
Mm.

207
00:14:50,167 --> 00:14:51,717
Kau jumpa North dari mana, wei?

208
00:14:53,277 --> 00:14:55,752
Aku sepak tanah sikit, dia muncul entah dari mana.

209
00:14:56,528 --> 00:14:57,887
Makhluk apa tu?

210
00:14:58,157 --> 00:15:00,010
Aku rasa macam—

211
00:15:00,905 --> 00:15:02,308
North ada tenaga positif sangat.

212
00:15:02,637 --> 00:15:05,405
Bagi aku, lebih kepada tenaga positif-negatif.

213
00:15:05,884 --> 00:15:07,675
Ya, ya, aku tahu.

214
00:15:09,314 --> 00:15:12,093
Aku harap aku pun boleh jadi tenaga positif untuk P'Fah.

215
00:15:13,148 --> 00:15:15,069
Walaupun aku tak sekuat North.

216
00:15:15,616 --> 00:15:18,001
Kenapa kau kena kuat?

217
00:15:18,044 --> 00:15:20,927
Macam aku cakap, jadi diri sendiri pun dah cukup.

218
00:15:21,164 --> 00:15:23,671
Jangan cuba jadi macam North.

219
00:15:27,189 --> 00:15:29,801
Jadi, keputusan exam med dah keluar, kan? Macam mana?

220
00:15:33,681 --> 00:15:35,158
Aku tak lepas.

221
00:15:41,525 --> 00:15:43,171
Tapi aku dah bersedia untuk tu.

222
00:15:43,810 --> 00:15:45,743
Rasanya tahun ni aku belum bersedia.

223
00:15:46,299 --> 00:15:48,214
Aku cuba lagi tahun depan.

224
00:15:48,711 --> 00:15:50,121
Jadi kenapa kau nak jadi doktor?

225
00:15:54,681 --> 00:15:56,045
Aku...

226
00:15:56,668 --> 00:15:58,582
Aku nak tunaikan impian Fun.

227
00:16:03,548 --> 00:16:05,943
Dan impian kau sendiri?

228
00:17:18,010 --> 00:17:28,580
Aku tak tahu. Aku tak pernah makan diri sendiri. Tapi coklat ni manisnya ngam. Sedap. Terima kasih.

229
00:17:56,802 --> 00:17:58,041
Sial.

230
00:17:58,551 --> 00:17:59,477
Hah?

231
00:18:01,965 --> 00:18:02,964
Dah pagi ke?

232
00:18:03,663 --> 00:18:06,072
Tengok sana—dah nak petang.

233
00:18:06,414 --> 00:18:08,401
Aku habis kelas balik, kau masih tidur.

234
00:18:09,134 --> 00:18:11,957
Sial—kau ambil kehadiran untuk aku ke tak?

235
00:18:15,607 --> 00:18:18,638
Jangan risau, kawan. Kau pun nak kena buang tak lama lagi.

236
00:18:18,845 --> 00:18:20,345
Kau ni, Fah. Menyampah.

237
00:18:23,496 --> 00:18:26,151
Huh.

238
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:31,530
- Sakit kepala?
- Mana ada.

239
00:18:33,954 --> 00:18:36,905
Nah, aku belikan kau makanan dan ubat mabuk.

240
00:18:37,355 --> 00:18:38,345
Makanlah.

241
00:18:42,715 --> 00:18:45,320
Terima kasih, bro. Kau memang baik gila.

242
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:58,034
Kenapa kau mabuk teruk macam ni?

243
00:19:02,114 --> 00:19:05,954
Fah, macam mana dengan orang yang hantar surat tu?

244
00:19:06,505 --> 00:19:07,688
Kau dah buka hati untuk dia?

245
00:19:10,146 --> 00:19:13,817
Ya. Aku rasa dia comel juga.

246
00:19:15,075 --> 00:19:17,660
Dan jujurnya, aku suka rasa biasa macam ni.

247
00:19:21,539 --> 00:19:22,327
Ops.

248
00:19:23,948 --> 00:19:25,028
Bil coklat.

249
00:19:27,782 --> 00:19:30,189
- Berapa?
- 550.

250
00:19:30,714 --> 00:19:33,053
- Okeylah. Tak mahal.
- Dolar.

251
00:19:34,214 --> 00:19:35,185
Dolar?

252
00:19:35,528 --> 00:19:37,290
Ya. Tambah 10 dolar caj bawa.

253
00:19:38,435 --> 00:19:41,179
- Cepat pindahkan.
- Kau dapat dari mana?

254
00:19:41,814 --> 00:19:42,927
Jangan tanya.

255
00:19:43,093 --> 00:19:44,755
- 18 ribu, kan?
- 20. Pindahkan.

256
00:19:44,862 --> 00:19:45,745
Mm.

257
00:19:46,642 --> 00:19:47,625
Dah pindah.

258
00:19:49,721 --> 00:19:52,343
Kau buka hati je dah habis 500 dolar.

259
00:19:53,851 --> 00:19:56,002
Semua kawan aku macam sugar daddy.

260
00:19:57,143 --> 00:19:59,401
Cakap macam kau bukan sama je?

261
00:19:59,804 --> 00:20:02,691
Tak mungkin. Aku tak bagi orang tumpang duit aku.

262
00:20:03,068 --> 00:20:04,791
Cinta ni mengarut.

263
00:20:05,244 --> 00:20:09,334
Cepat makan. Kalau kau keluar, kunci bilik untuk aku.

264
00:20:09,911 --> 00:20:11,148
Aku sambung belajar.

265
00:20:14,991 --> 00:20:15,869
Kemas sekali.

266
00:20:16,394 --> 00:20:17,176
Mm.

267
00:20:30,708 --> 00:20:32,435
Fah, boleh pinjam baju?

268
00:20:32,831 --> 00:20:33,580
Mm.

269
00:21:01,511 --> 00:21:03,057
Kenapa kau baca banyak sangat, Fah?

270
00:21:03,850 --> 00:21:05,533
Aku ringkaskan apa yang kita belajar hari ni.

271
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:08,342
Kau ponteng kelas—kau pun kena ulang kaji.

272
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,860
Mestilah aku buat. Kau tak penat ke?

273
00:21:10,860 --> 00:21:13,000
Mestilah aku penat.

274
00:21:15,703 --> 00:21:17,068
Jadi Tonfah memang memenatkan, ya?

275
00:21:20,228 --> 00:21:22,583
Ya, jadi Tonfah memang penat gila.

276
00:21:22,899 --> 00:21:24,143
Kalau jadi Arthit, penat juga?

277
00:21:24,945 --> 00:21:25,900
Aku?

278
00:21:27,072 --> 00:21:29,074
Memang teruk gila.

279
00:21:29,817 --> 00:21:31,001
Apa yang teruk?

280
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:33,423
Semua.

281
00:21:36,528 --> 00:21:37,631
Hei, Fah.

282
00:21:37,774 --> 00:21:38,161
Ya?

283
00:21:38,349 --> 00:21:44,146
Ingat tak Hill kata kalau dia gabungkan kau dengan aku—

284
00:21:44,628 --> 00:21:47,103
dia akan dapat seorang yang sempurna?

285
00:21:47,568 --> 00:21:48,671
Mm.

286
00:21:50,844 --> 00:21:54,331
Tapi jujurnya, aku tak nak digabungkan dengan kau.

287
00:21:55,291 --> 00:21:57,207
Aku cuma buat perbandingan, bodoh.

288
00:21:58,665 --> 00:22:00,237
Aku pun tak nak digabungkan dengan kau.

289
00:22:00,297 --> 00:22:01,071
Alah.

290
00:22:08,477 --> 00:22:09,816
Kau masih belum berhenti lagi?

291
00:22:10,168 --> 00:22:11,782
Tabiat paksa diri sendiri tu.

292
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:17,117
Ya.

293
00:22:27,870 --> 00:22:29,640
Kalau ada apa-apa, beritahu aku, Fah.

294
00:22:34,241 --> 00:22:35,774
Cakap saja, Fah.

295
00:22:36,730 --> 00:22:38,260
Aku nak ambil tahu hal kau.

296
00:22:45,859 --> 00:22:47,725
Aku cuma tak nak kecewakan sesiapa.

297
00:22:49,583 --> 00:22:50,902
Ayah aku...

298
00:22:51,634 --> 00:22:53,777
Dia nak aku jadi langit yang lebih tinggi dari semua.

299
00:22:54,474 --> 00:22:55,411
Untuk mak aku,

300
00:22:56,408 --> 00:23:00,165
dia nak aku jadi macam pokok tempat orang bersandar.

301
00:23:01,294 --> 00:23:02,727
Jadi aku jadi Tonfah.

302
00:23:05,591 --> 00:23:07,814
Apa-apa pun, kenapa nama kau Arthit?

303
00:23:08,997 --> 00:23:10,280
Aku lahir hari Ahad.

304
00:23:10,866 --> 00:23:11,764
Mudah saja, kan?

305
00:23:12,105 --> 00:23:14,740
Ya, hidup tak perlu rumit sangat, Fah.

306
00:23:17,785 --> 00:23:18,709
Jadi,

307
00:23:19,632 --> 00:23:21,321
dua-dua mak ayah aku doktor.

308
00:23:21,752 --> 00:23:24,574
Mereka baik dan mesra.

309
00:23:25,573 --> 00:23:27,294
Dan mereka sangat ambil berat orang sekeliling.

310
00:23:28,195 --> 00:23:31,568
Kau tahu, mereka jarang paksa aku buat apa-apa.

311
00:23:32,437 --> 00:23:33,982
Aku membesar jadi macam mereka.

312
00:23:35,268 --> 00:23:40,466
Jadi aku dah biasa tanya orang lain okey ke tak.

313
00:23:41,842 --> 00:23:43,094
Macam,

314
00:23:44,192 --> 00:23:45,856
tak boleh ke sekali-sekala tak peduli?

315
00:23:48,853 --> 00:23:50,733
Aku dah cuba, tau.

316
00:23:51,044 --> 00:23:54,244
Tapi aku selalu ikut harapan orang.

317
00:23:57,037 --> 00:23:58,208
Sampai kadang-kadang

318
00:23:58,874 --> 00:24:00,362
aku pun tak tahu

319
00:24:01,336 --> 00:24:02,925
aku nak jadi orang macam mana.

320
00:24:04,819 --> 00:24:06,471
Jadi... kau bahagia sekarang?

321
00:24:12,531 --> 00:24:13,259
Ya.

322
00:24:14,450 --> 00:24:15,700
Nampak? Kau tu.

323
00:24:15,974 --> 00:24:17,259
Ada orang

324
00:24:18,700 --> 00:24:20,228
langsung tak tahu dia lahir untuk apa.

325
00:24:20,914 --> 00:24:22,026
Macam aku.

326
00:24:23,684 --> 00:24:25,376
Bila aku suruh kau jadi diri sendiri,

327
00:24:26,121 --> 00:24:29,911
bukan maksud aku kau kena lain atau hidup untuk diri saja.

328
00:24:31,626 --> 00:24:35,851
Bagi sesetengah orang, ambil berat orang pun dah cukup.

329
00:24:36,536 --> 00:24:38,958
Sial, bila kau serius,

330
00:24:39,300 --> 00:24:41,275
kau bunyi macam sangat matang.

331
00:24:43,195 --> 00:24:44,017
Yalah,

332
00:24:45,260 --> 00:24:48,754
Aku jenis serius—cuma tak pandai tunjuk.

333
00:24:50,348 --> 00:24:51,290
Apa maksudnya tu?

334
00:24:51,722 --> 00:24:54,320
Maksud aku,

335
00:24:54,509 --> 00:24:57,285
asal kau hidup bahagia, itu dah cukup.

336
00:24:57,401 --> 00:24:58,057
Er...

337
00:24:58,540 --> 00:25:01,408
Kalau penat, rehat. Tak semestinya kena belajar selalu.

338
00:25:01,705 --> 00:25:03,294
Belajar pun tak semestinya terus jadi pandai.

339
00:25:03,770 --> 00:25:06,592
Atau kau boleh buat tak kisah macam aku.

340
00:25:07,579 --> 00:25:08,656
Er...

341
00:25:09,379 --> 00:25:12,177
Aku gerak dulu. Jumpa lagi.

342
00:25:12,469 --> 00:25:14,472
Terima kasih, bro.

343
00:25:31,588 --> 00:25:32,977
Jadi apa kesimpulan kau sebenarnya?

344
00:25:34,762 --> 00:25:36,527
Coklat 18,000 baht.

345
00:25:37,998 --> 00:25:40,277
Kalau Johan yang beli, aku tak terkejut pun.

346
00:25:40,299 --> 00:25:41,368
Tapi bila kau...

347
00:25:42,601 --> 00:25:43,494
Ya.

348
00:25:43,961 --> 00:25:45,838
Aku cuma nak beli saja.

349
00:25:46,099 --> 00:25:46,979
Itu saja.

350
00:25:47,352 --> 00:25:49,711
Kalau dia kata tak suka, maknanya dia tak suka.

351
00:25:49,915 --> 00:25:52,847
Coklat Perancis. Cuma tanda ikhlas.

352
00:25:52,877 --> 00:25:55,096
“Tanda ikhlas” kau tu memang keterlaluan.

353
00:25:55,948 --> 00:25:58,822
Serius, pelik sangat ke? Cuma coklat saja.

354
00:25:59,248 --> 00:26:01,189
Tak pelik. Normal sangat.

355
00:26:02,576 --> 00:26:04,117
Kalau untuk orang yang kau suka.

356
00:26:08,125 --> 00:26:10,459
Jadi macam mana, ha, Fah?

357
00:26:11,810 --> 00:26:12,551
Err...

358
00:26:13,791 --> 00:26:15,317
Aku suka dia. Jadi kenapa?

359
00:26:19,234 --> 00:26:20,188
Sejauh mana kau suka dia?

360
00:26:23,325 --> 00:26:25,546
Aku tak tahu. Aku cuma suka.

361
00:26:25,914 --> 00:26:28,496
Aku tak tahu nak ukur macam mana.

362
00:26:30,229 --> 00:26:33,422
Boleh ke suka orang yang kau tak pernah jumpa?

363
00:26:34,434 --> 00:26:36,108
Rasanya bahagian tu tak penting sangat bagi aku.

364
00:26:36,468 --> 00:26:37,845
Cukup dia itu dia.

365
00:26:38,967 --> 00:26:40,346
Orang dalam surat-surat tu.

366
00:26:41,718 --> 00:26:43,157
Itu dah cukup untuk aku.

367
00:26:47,595 --> 00:26:51,760
Bila fikir balik, hubungan korang tak stabil pun.

368
00:26:52,402 --> 00:26:56,145
Kalau dia hilang, dia boleh hilang macam tu saja.

369
00:26:57,416 --> 00:27:03,189
Dan kalau suatu hari dia sedar orang dekat lebih nyata dari surat,

370
00:27:03,678 --> 00:27:07,441
dia boleh hilang, dan kau pun tak layak kejar dia.

371
00:27:10,595 --> 00:27:14,013
Lepas semua ni, kau betul-betul okey biar macam ni?

372
00:27:23,020 --> 00:27:24,192
Fah.

373
00:27:25,333 --> 00:27:26,487
Aku lapar.

374
00:27:28,312 --> 00:27:30,405
- Ada apa-apa tak kena?
- Ada orang suruh saya bagi ini pada awak.

375
00:27:32,054 --> 00:27:33,103
Daripada siapa?

376
00:27:33,383 --> 00:27:38,060
Dari kawan saya. Dia minta jangan sebut nama, tapi dia kata selamat menjamu selera.

377
00:27:38,358 --> 00:27:39,240
Faham.

378
00:27:39,635 --> 00:27:41,955
Saya betul-betul tak boleh terima. Tolong cakap maaf.

379
00:27:42,561 --> 00:27:44,816
Tolong terima. Kawan saya sangat suka awak.

380
00:27:45,235 --> 00:27:47,774
Saya betul-betul tak boleh. Maaf.

381
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:50,890
Saya faham.

382
00:27:53,940 --> 00:27:57,161
Fah, kenapa dengan kau? Kau biasa terima barang orang, kan?

383
00:27:57,280 --> 00:27:59,767
Bukan kau kata kalau orang bagi, kena terima?

384
00:28:00,062 --> 00:28:01,017
Kalau tak terima, kurang ajar.

385
00:28:01,207 --> 00:28:02,708
Itu masa aku dah ada orang dalam hati.

386
00:28:03,352 --> 00:28:04,850
Macam mana aku boleh terima dari sesiapa saja?

387
00:28:05,265 --> 00:28:06,216
Kan?

388
00:28:06,666 --> 00:28:07,337
Ya.

389
00:28:14,468 --> 00:28:17,259
Fah, tak boleh ke kau ambil? Kalau itu makanan?

390
00:28:17,272 --> 00:28:19,028
Kau muncul dari mana, lapar macam tu?

391
00:28:19,552 --> 00:28:21,128
Aku bukan minta barang kau. Aku minta barang dia.

392
00:28:21,177 --> 00:28:23,647
- Itu barang dia, kau tahu kan?
- Aku cuma lapar.

393
00:28:24,434 --> 00:28:26,711
Ya, aku pun memang nak pergi sana.

394
00:28:28,444 --> 00:28:30,346
Hah? Apa?

395
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:32,383
Kemalangan kereta?

396
00:28:32,598 --> 00:28:38,960
Ya. Kaki aku bersimen, terperap dalam bilik. Mungkin tak ke uni sekejap. Maaf.

397
00:28:39,250 --> 00:28:41,429
Nampaknya aku tak dapat hantar pada P'Tonfah.

398
00:28:41,637 --> 00:28:44,305
Habis hadiah aku— eh, tunggu.

399
00:28:45,130 --> 00:28:46,290
Cupid dah tak boleh jalan.

400
00:28:46,810 --> 00:28:48,330
Dia tak boleh jalankan misi.

401
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:49,780
Kita nak buat macam mana?

402
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:56,280
Tak ada orang lain boleh ganti dia?

403
00:28:58,790 --> 00:28:59,810
Kenapa kau buat macam tu?

404
00:29:01,470 --> 00:29:02,960
Kau ingat senang nak cari orang?

405
00:29:03,350 --> 00:29:06,110
Lama gila nak cari orang sesuai untuk misi besar ni.

406
00:29:06,190 --> 00:29:07,580
Dan nak runding semua benda pun ambil masa.

407
00:29:07,840 --> 00:29:12,420
- Kau ingat sesiapa pun boleh?
- Aku tahu, okey? Aku pun stres.

408
00:29:17,420 --> 00:29:18,840
- Phoon.
- Hmm?

409
00:29:19,010 --> 00:29:21,080
Apa kata kita guna peluang ni untuk uji P'Fah?

410
00:29:21,950 --> 00:29:24,700
Kalau P'Fah tak dapat apa-apa dari kau dan mula resah,

411
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:26,410
itu sebenarnya benda baik.

412
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:27,850
Er...

413
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:30,220
Tapi aku tak nak uji P'Fah.

414
00:29:30,430 --> 00:29:33,640
Jadi nak buat apa? Tunggu kaki Bobby sembuh?

415
00:29:33,770 --> 00:29:35,110
Itu lama gila.

416
00:29:37,090 --> 00:29:38,850
Aku rasa kita kena tukar rancangan.

417
00:29:39,310 --> 00:29:42,010
Macam mana kalau tetapkan tempat dan bergilir tukar barang?

418
00:29:42,520 --> 00:29:45,130
Hah? Kalau korang terserempak macam mana?

419
00:29:47,100 --> 00:29:49,960
Kalau P'Fah dan maew setuju masa,

420
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:51,630
korang mungkin takkan jumpa.

421
00:29:52,190 --> 00:29:53,820
Tapi kalau aku P'Fah,

422
00:29:54,590 --> 00:29:57,220
aku mesti nak intai diam-diam siapa orang tu.

423
00:29:57,790 --> 00:29:58,660
Mm.

424
00:29:59,220 --> 00:30:00,740
Aku rasa P'Fah takkan buat macam tu, 100 peratus.

425
00:30:01,250 --> 00:30:03,980
Kalau dia nak tahu, dari dulu lagi dia dah tanya.

426
00:30:04,630 --> 00:30:06,960
Dia sangat hormat orang dalam surat tu.

427
00:30:09,460 --> 00:30:10,900
Tapi cara ni nampak okey.

428
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:13,100
Tapi takkan itu menyusahkan dia?

429
00:30:13,460 --> 00:30:17,160
Alah, kita dah sejauh ni. Kuatkan diri.

430
00:30:18,430 --> 00:30:20,040
Jangan mengalah lagi.

431
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:23,620
Aku rasa rancangan Dao memang jadi.

432
00:30:23,890 --> 00:30:26,980
Kalau risau pasal P'Fah, jumpa dia di bangunan perubatan.

433
00:30:27,170 --> 00:30:28,500
Mana-mana kedai kopi pun boleh.

434
00:30:28,760 --> 00:30:29,830
Senang untuk P'Fah macam tu.

435
00:30:30,740 --> 00:30:31,180
Betul?

436
00:30:31,290 --> 00:30:33,410
Tapi kedai kopi selalu sesak.

437
00:30:38,060 --> 00:30:39,240
Kenapa dengan kau sekarang?

438
00:30:39,460 --> 00:30:43,350
Aku cakap ni, aku dah jumpa Cupid baru untuk korang.

439
00:30:45,900 --> 00:30:46,730
Siapa?

440
00:30:47,150 --> 00:30:48,320
Ya, siapa?

441
00:30:51,040 --> 00:30:52,400
Kau serius?

442
00:30:55,610 --> 00:30:56,240
Ya.

443
00:30:57,770 --> 00:30:59,410
P'Gib, ini menyusahkan kau tak?

444
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:02,230
Tak langsung. Aku on.

445
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,680
Macam seronok.

446
00:31:04,030 --> 00:31:05,780
Aku tak pernah buat benda macam ni.

447
00:31:07,250 --> 00:31:08,390
North.

448
00:31:08,890 --> 00:31:10,280
Kau betul-betul kenal semua orang kat kampus?

449
00:31:10,370 --> 00:31:12,680
Nampak? Aku dah cakap, percaya aku.

450
00:31:13,320 --> 00:31:16,890
Fah memang datang kafe aku tiap pagi.

451
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:18,410
Memang ngam dengan rancangan kita.

452
00:31:18,810 --> 00:31:20,110
Aku nak cakap ni pada korang.

453
00:31:20,300 --> 00:31:23,060
P'Gib cantik dan kaya,

454
00:31:23,350 --> 00:31:27,580
pandai buat kopi—paling penting, pandai merancang.

455
00:31:29,410 --> 00:31:34,000
Wah, tak tahu kau puji ikhlas atau nak kupon diskaun.

456
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:36,120
Mungkin yang kedua.

457
00:31:36,460 --> 00:31:37,430
Aku ikhlas.

458
00:31:38,490 --> 00:31:40,150
- Tapi kupon pun bagus.
- Nampak?

459
00:31:40,390 --> 00:31:41,910
Aku dah agak—memang macam kau.

460
00:31:48,950 --> 00:31:51,370
Wei, North. Itu cawan aku. Cawan kau sana.

461
00:31:51,380 --> 00:31:53,030
- Aku rasa sikit je.
- Habis tu kenapa tak order koko?

462
00:31:53,130 --> 00:31:55,120
- Tak boleh rasa pun?
- Tak, aku kedekut.

463
00:31:55,520 --> 00:31:57,350
Kalau P'Hill dengan P'Fah tak muncul macam mana?

464
00:31:57,790 --> 00:31:58,910
Kita nak serah pada nasib je?

465
00:31:59,170 --> 00:32:00,850
Kalau P'Fah tak datang esok pun,

466
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:02,160
dia akan datang hari lain.

467
00:32:02,300 --> 00:32:04,640
Aku rasa P'Fah takkan berhenti minum kopi sini.

468
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:05,950
Sebab P'Gib tuang sikit sangat.

469
00:32:06,610 --> 00:32:09,520
Mungkin aku tak payah belanja kau kek lagi.

470
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:11,110
Aku baru nak belanja kau.

471
00:32:11,730 --> 00:32:14,130
- Aku tak terlibat, okey?
- Aku gurau je, P'Gib.

472
00:32:14,570 --> 00:32:17,210
Aku dah cakap jangan rapat sangat dengan Arthit.

473
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:20,400
Mula-mula dulu kau comel sangat.

474
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:21,780
Betul tu.

475
00:32:21,970 --> 00:32:23,680
Semua ni salah P'Arthit.

476
00:32:24,190 --> 00:32:26,250
Sampai cemarkan orang suci macam aku.

477
00:32:26,470 --> 00:32:27,610
Macam mana kau boleh cakap macam tu, North?

478
00:32:27,870 --> 00:32:30,940
Kau? Aku cuma nampak kau elok bila P'Johan ada.

479
00:32:31,190 --> 00:32:32,740
Selain tu—kau memang huru-hara!

480
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:36,580
“Pure” konon. Dah kotor pun sebenarnya.

481
00:32:36,620 --> 00:32:38,510
Aku yang akan buat kau lagi teruk.

482
00:32:38,670 --> 00:32:41,440
Tunggu aku pergi tandas dulu.

483
00:32:44,410 --> 00:32:46,650
Eh—kau okey?

484
00:32:46,850 --> 00:32:47,700
Aku okey.

485
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:55,120
Maaf aku tak dapat hubungi kau beberapa hari.
Orang yang patut serahkan barang tu tak ada.

486
00:32:55,157 --> 00:33:02,857
Jadi aku minta tolong P'Gib.
Menyusahkan tak kalau kau ambil sini tiap pagi?

487
00:33:02,872 --> 00:33:04,777
Kalau tak senang, tak apa.

488
00:33:04,990 --> 00:33:08,822
Cuaca kebelakangan ni tak menentu. Jaga kesihatan ya.

489
00:33:08,826 --> 00:33:11,431
Aku rasa aku pun macam nak jatuh sakit.

490
00:33:11,644 --> 00:33:15,607
Aku dah order kopi panas untuk kau. Jangan order lagi—secawan cukup.

491
00:33:16,730 --> 00:33:19,570
- Nah, Fah. Kopi panas kau.
- Terima kasih.

492
00:33:22,077 --> 00:33:24,170
- Err, Mhor.
- Ya?

493
00:33:24,490 --> 00:33:26,020
Kau nak cari dia?

494
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:28,960
Aku rasa itu bukan idea yang bagus.

495
00:33:31,610 --> 00:33:35,520
Bagus. Kalau kau jadi ingin tahu dan asak aku,

496
00:33:35,760 --> 00:33:37,430
aku akan jadi serba salah.

497
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,480
Tapi—

498
00:33:40,890 --> 00:33:42,490
Aku bagi spoiler sikitlah.

499
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:45,160
Apa dia?

500
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:48,870
Dia...

501
00:33:49,450 --> 00:33:51,240
seorang yang sangat baik.

502
00:33:53,350 --> 00:33:56,290
Kalau pasal tu, aku dah tahu.

503
00:33:58,730 --> 00:34:01,350
Lepas ni nak buat apa? Rasanya aku buat kopi lagi.

504
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:06,780
Dia hilang ke mana? Dia suruh aku beli, lepas tu tak muncul.

505
00:34:06,910 --> 00:34:08,170
Dia kata dia pergi kedai ubat.

506
00:34:08,520 --> 00:34:09,440
Siapa yang sakit?

507
00:34:11,040 --> 00:34:14,866
Oh—kalau dia tak datang, aku makan dulu. Aku tak boleh tunggu lagi. Oops.

508
00:34:15,315 --> 00:34:16,964
Itu aku punya.

509
00:34:18,110 --> 00:34:21,060
Kau belum sampai. Aku takut dia jadi sejuk.

510
00:34:21,240 --> 00:34:23,200
Jadi aku nak makan untuk kau je—itu saja.

511
00:34:23,650 --> 00:34:26,020
Jadi kesimpulannya—kita nak tunggu diam-diam?

512
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:29,050
Tak.

513
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:31,570
Kau tak nak tahu siapa dia?

514
00:34:33,100 --> 00:34:35,330
Jelas dia tak nak aku tahu.

515
00:34:36,020 --> 00:34:38,150
Patutnya aku fikir keselesaan dia dulu, kan?

516
00:34:42,410 --> 00:34:43,680
Habis tu, yang tu apa?

517
00:34:43,990 --> 00:34:45,460
Oh, dia tak sihat.

518
00:34:45,770 --> 00:34:46,950
Oh.

519
00:35:00,770 --> 00:35:03,330
Kau datang lambat sangat—aku dah nak tutup kedai.

520
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:07,220
Nah.

521
00:35:17,070 --> 00:35:17,850
Phoon.

522
00:35:18,690 --> 00:35:19,990
Kau sakit ke?

523
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:22,140
Sikit je.

524
00:35:24,330 --> 00:35:27,120
Jangan risau pasal orang sangat sampai lupa jaga diri.

525
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:29,530
Terima kasih.

526
00:35:33,520 --> 00:35:34,660
Kau patut jumpa doktor?

527
00:35:52,106 --> 00:35:55,693
Untuk pesakit: Aku tak pasti kau dah lega atau belum,

528
00:35:56,008 --> 00:35:59,422
tapi tolong pantau simptom dan makan ubat ikut arahan.

529
00:36:00,054 --> 00:36:05,131
P.S. Jangan risau. Aku dah tanya mak cik aku, ahli farmasi.

530
00:36:05,475 --> 00:36:08,300
Kalau tak makin baik, tolong jumpa doktor.

531
00:36:09,023 --> 00:36:12,185
Kalau kecemasan, kau boleh telefon aku nombor ni.

532
00:36:22,090 --> 00:36:25,281
- Salin untuk cuci hidung
- Garam rehidrasi oral: 1 sachet/600 ml, hirup sikit-sikit
- Tampalan gel sejuk sampai suhu badan turun
- Lozenge tekak: satu biji sekali

533
00:36:41,270 --> 00:36:43,520
Helo, Foam. Kau kat mana sekarang?

534
00:36:43,810 --> 00:36:48,463
Eh, bukan kau kata kau sakit?
Kau bunyi ceria—dah baik ke?

535
00:36:49,370 --> 00:36:51,280
Aku dapat ubat yang bagus.

536
00:36:51,909 --> 00:36:52,914
Ubat apa?

537
00:36:54,210 --> 00:36:55,380
Tak nak bagitahu.

538
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:59,210
Tunggu sekejap—ada panggilan masuk lain.

539
00:37:02,830 --> 00:37:03,540
Helo?

540
00:37:03,560 --> 00:37:07,510
Maaf, ini nombor Typhoon ke?

541
00:37:09,310 --> 00:37:10,420
Ya, betul.

542
00:37:10,780 --> 00:37:11,960
Siapa ni?

543
00:37:24,240 --> 00:37:25,610
Typhoon, sayang.

544
00:37:28,190 --> 00:37:30,860
Maaf kalau ini buat kau tak selesa.

545
00:37:31,980 --> 00:37:33,610
Aku okey.

546
00:37:35,870 --> 00:37:38,530
Awak datang Chiang Mai dengan ayah saya?

547
00:37:39,330 --> 00:37:42,690
Saya dengar dia ada klien di sini,

548
00:37:42,990 --> 00:37:44,840
sebab tu dia selalu datang.

549
00:37:45,870 --> 00:37:48,720
Tak. Saya datang sini nak jumpa awak, Typhoon.

550
00:37:52,380 --> 00:37:54,580
Ada apa yang awak nak cakap dengan saya?

551
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,540
Awak dah tahu, kan,

552
00:37:57,670 --> 00:37:59,410
yang ayah awak kahwin dengan saya?

553
00:38:05,070 --> 00:38:05,990
Ya.

554
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:11,190
Tapi dia tak pernah beritahu saya dia dah ada keluarga dulu.

555
00:38:12,970 --> 00:38:14,740
Saya baru tahu kebelakangan ni.

556
00:38:18,170 --> 00:38:20,840
Awak tak boleh terima dia pernah ada keluarga dulu, ya?

557
00:38:21,780 --> 00:38:23,690
Yang dia dah ada keluarga.

558
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:25,700
Saya okey—

559
00:38:26,540 --> 00:38:30,060
kalau dia tak menipu dan tinggalkan anak sendiri macam ni.

560
00:38:31,530 --> 00:38:32,430
P'Rit.

561
00:38:33,690 --> 00:38:35,190
Dia pernah jaga awak tak?

562
00:38:49,580 --> 00:38:51,560
Saya tangkap dia curang.

563
00:38:56,820 --> 00:38:57,890
Saya minta maaf.

564
00:38:58,440 --> 00:38:59,960
Saya sampai menangis depan awak.

565
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,650
Tak apa.

566
00:39:05,140 --> 00:39:06,810
Jadi saya upah orang siasat dia,

567
00:39:07,920 --> 00:39:09,330
dan dari situ saya tahu—

568
00:39:10,530 --> 00:39:12,560
bukan saja dia ada hubungan sulit,

569
00:39:13,330 --> 00:39:15,050
dia juga pernah ada keluarga dulu,

570
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:17,790
dan ada seorang anak lelaki lagi.

571
00:39:19,190 --> 00:39:20,950
Saya sedang buat keputusan

572
00:39:22,450 --> 00:39:24,410
keputusan paling penting dalam hidup saya.

573
00:39:25,240 --> 00:39:30,660
Saya cuma nak tahu dia boleh jadi ayah yang baik untuk anak saya.

574
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:35,420
Saya tak tahu

575
00:39:36,390 --> 00:39:39,120
sama ada ayah saya boleh jadi ayah yang baik untuk anak awak,

576
00:39:40,460 --> 00:39:41,890
tapi untuk saya,

577
00:39:42,660 --> 00:39:43,830
dia tak pernah berjaya jadi ayah yang baik.

578
00:39:48,650 --> 00:39:49,780
Saya faham.

579
00:40:05,200 --> 00:40:06,190
Nama dia Fai.

580
00:40:09,100 --> 00:40:10,080
Fai.

581
00:40:14,110 --> 00:40:16,020
Adik perempuan P'Phoon.

582
00:40:16,120 --> 00:40:17,290
Helo.

583
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:21,890
Adik tiri saya bernama Fun.

584
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:24,980
Betul? Kebetulan sungguh.

585
00:40:25,520 --> 00:40:28,020
Saya namakan dia "Phafai"

586
00:40:28,370 --> 00:40:30,350
supaya sepadan dengan nama saya, Phaphrae.

587
00:40:31,330 --> 00:40:33,730
Phafai? Comelnya nama tu.

588
00:40:34,290 --> 00:40:35,770
Terima kasih.

589
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:38,490
Jadi, di mana Fun?

590
00:40:43,250 --> 00:40:45,360
Fun dah meninggal dunia.

591
00:40:47,700 --> 00:40:48,880
Saya minta maaf.

592
00:40:53,730 --> 00:40:54,720
Tak apa.

593
00:40:56,170 --> 00:40:58,260
Walau sedih sebab saya takkan jumpa dia lagi,

594
00:40:58,990 --> 00:41:00,520
bila teringatkan Fun

595
00:41:01,090 --> 00:41:02,370
itu bukan perkara buruk pun.

596
00:41:04,410 --> 00:41:07,840
Awak dan Fun mesti sangat sayang satu sama lain.

597
00:41:11,260 --> 00:41:14,100
Saya buat perkara teruk pada Fun sebelum dia meninggal.

598
00:41:15,430 --> 00:41:17,140
Saya pun tak sempat minta maaf.

599
00:41:18,100 --> 00:41:21,500
Jadi sekarang, saya tebus kesilapan saya dengan

600
00:41:22,690 --> 00:41:23,970
hidup untuk Fun.

601
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:30,330
Saya rasa kakak awak lebih nak awak hidup untuk diri sendiri.

602
00:41:31,590 --> 00:41:32,660
Saya pergi dulu.

603
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:34,960
Kalau apa-apa jadi, awak boleh telefon saya bila-bila.

604
00:41:35,280 --> 00:41:36,380
Terima kasih banyak-banyak.

605
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:37,440
Jom.

606
00:41:48,110 --> 00:41:50,850
Hidup untuk diri sendiri... apa maksudnya, Fun?

607
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:08,140
Saya rasa kakak awak lebih nak awak hidup untuk diri sendiri.

608
00:42:08,470 --> 00:42:11,050
Habis tu, macam mana dengan impian awak?

609
00:42:13,490 --> 00:42:14,730
Awak belajar di fakulti apa?

610
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:16,700
Perubatan Veterinar.

611
00:42:18,950 --> 00:42:21,110
P'Fah ingat Phoon tak suka bidang ni.

612
00:42:37,270 --> 00:42:38,430
Teh pic awak dah siap.

613
00:42:39,470 --> 00:42:42,700
Yang ni percuma. Fah belanja.

614
00:42:43,150 --> 00:42:45,830
Dia pun tinggal banyak duit. Nak apa lagi?

615
00:42:51,890 --> 00:42:52,850
Boleh saya duduk sini?

616
00:42:53,120 --> 00:42:54,550
Oh... boleh.

617
00:43:00,120 --> 00:43:04,070
Phoon, awak betul-betul tak nak Fah tahu awak penulis surat tu?

618
00:43:05,870 --> 00:43:06,720
Tak juga.

619
00:43:07,840 --> 00:43:12,540
Entahlah... saya rasa hubungan bila seorang tahu semua

620
00:43:12,730 --> 00:43:14,200
tapi seorang lagi tak tahu apa-apa

621
00:43:15,130 --> 00:43:16,340
macam sedih.

622
00:43:17,740 --> 00:43:20,520
Fah nampak macam sangat suka awak.

623
00:43:21,820 --> 00:43:23,350
Awak rasa dia rasa macam mana

624
00:43:23,630 --> 00:43:25,940
kalau dia tak tahu apa-apa pasal orang yang dia suka?

625
00:43:32,290 --> 00:43:34,940
Maaf, saya merepek je.

626
00:43:35,940 --> 00:43:38,410
Err, saya sambung kerja dulu.

627
00:43:38,540 --> 00:43:40,630
Awak boleh minum sekarang.

628
00:43:44,851 --> 00:43:47,632
Saya baru buat keputusan penting dalam hidup saya.

629
00:43:47,687 --> 00:43:53,991
Saya tak boleh cakap apa, tapi teringat awak buat saya lebih berani.

630
00:43:54,490 --> 00:43:57,517
Jadi saya cuma nak ucap terima kasih. Terima kasih banyak.

631
00:44:01,360 --> 00:44:05,025
Saya tak tahu berita baik apa, tapi tahniah.

632
00:44:05,041 --> 00:44:07,331
Anggaplah ini hadiah tahniah daripada saya.

633
00:44:31,225 --> 00:44:33,200
Phoon, esok hari jadi P'Fah ke?

634
00:44:33,680 --> 00:44:35,259
Macam mana awak tahu?

635
00:44:37,382 --> 00:44:43,200
P'Hill bawa saya pilih hadiah untuk P'Fah. Awak pun ambil peluang ni.

636
00:44:43,558 --> 00:44:45,866
Saya dah sediakan hadiah hari jadi untuk P'Fah.

637
00:44:48,088 --> 00:44:50,408
Daripada Typhoon, atau daripada penulis surat tu?

638
00:44:53,997 --> 00:44:54,982
Dua-dua.

639
00:45:43,085 --> 00:45:46,810
Baju ni cantik, tapi longgar sangat. Saya tak boleh pakai keluar.

640
00:45:47,087 --> 00:45:50,521
Maaf. Patutnya dulu saya minum susu lebih masa kecil.

641
00:45:50,706 --> 00:45:53,320
Tapi saya suka sangat. Saya pakai tidur.

642
00:45:53,530 --> 00:45:56,940
Awak baik sangat. Terima kasih banyak.

643
00:46:20,910 --> 00:46:22,680
Nah—selamat hari jadi.

644
00:46:22,910 --> 00:46:24,060
Terima kasih.

645
00:46:24,616 --> 00:46:26,980
- Ini daripada saya dan Ter sekali.
- Terima kasih banyak.

646
00:46:42,270 --> 00:46:44,190
Selamat hari jadi.

647
00:46:45,880 --> 00:46:47,010
Terima kasih.

648
00:46:51,720 --> 00:46:53,600
Saya pergi tandas dulu.

649
00:47:04,600 --> 00:47:09,650
Aduh, Fah. Hari jadi kau,
tapi bukan pergi bar,

650
00:47:09,980 --> 00:47:11,670
kau heret aku ke sini untuk mengajar.

651
00:47:12,500 --> 00:47:13,380
Nah.

652
00:47:13,820 --> 00:47:14,930
Terima kasih.

653
00:47:15,170 --> 00:47:17,280
Tapi lain kali tak payah pun.

654
00:47:19,000 --> 00:47:19,750
Nah.

655
00:47:21,860 --> 00:47:22,920
Selamat Hari Jadi, P'Fah.

656
00:47:23,080 --> 00:47:24,040
Terima kasih.

657
00:47:50,940 --> 00:47:53,310
Tolong! Tolong!

658
00:47:53,360 --> 00:47:55,030
Ada orang tersekat dalam sini!

659
00:48:01,510 --> 00:48:04,730
P'Fah, tolong Phoon. Saya takut.

660
00:48:05,050 --> 00:48:06,910
P'Fah!

661
00:48:08,050 --> 00:48:11,410
P'Fah, tolong Phoon. Saya takut.

662
00:48:12,690 --> 00:48:13,700
P'Fah!

663
00:48:16,920 --> 00:48:18,920
P'Fah, tolong Phoon. Saya takut.

664
00:48:20,180 --> 00:48:21,120
Phoon.

665
00:48:29,620 --> 00:48:32,130
Phoon, undur dulu dari pintu tu.

666
00:48:43,450 --> 00:48:47,530
P'Fah, maaf. Saya buat salah.

667
00:48:48,110 --> 00:48:49,930
P'Fah marah saya ke?

668
00:48:50,820 --> 00:48:51,860
Dah tak apa.

669
00:48:52,410 --> 00:48:54,400
P'Fah ada sini.

670
00:48:57,460 --> 00:48:58,820
Saya ada sini.

671
00:48:59,980 --> 00:49:04,070
P'Fah marah saya ke? Tolong jangan marah saya.

672
00:49:04,420 --> 00:49:06,800
Bertenang dulu, ya? Awak dah selamat.

673
00:49:08,080 --> 00:49:09,470
Bertenang.

674
00:49:11,000 --> 00:49:13,000
Saya takut.

675
00:49:36,790 --> 00:49:40,090
P'Fah, maaf. Saya buat salah.

676
00:50:54,750 --> 00:50:57,320
Dulu saya anggap Phoon cuma adik.

677
00:50:58,010 --> 00:50:59,820
Budak sebelah rumah yang saya nak jaga sebaiknya.

678
00:51:00,600 --> 00:51:03,090
Tapi awak tahu dia tak anggap awak sekadar abang, kan?

679
00:51:03,260 --> 00:51:06,160
Dengan P'Fah... mungkin dah takkan sama lagi.

680
00:51:06,830 --> 00:51:11,270
Jadi awak nak beritahu P'Fah pasal P'Fun?

681
00:51:11,550 --> 00:51:13,560
Saya rasa P'Fah pun tergila-gilakan awak.

682
00:51:14,560 --> 00:51:15,720
Apa saja awak cakap, dia akan ikut.

683
00:51:16,100 --> 00:51:19,370
Pernah tak orang cakap awak comel sangat?

684
00:51:20,390 --> 00:51:21,950
Saya sangat suka bibir awak yang lembut

685
00:51:22,610 --> 00:51:23,810
bila saya cium awak.

